headline: Alliant Energy (LNT) Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates
summary: Alliant Energy (LNT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 2.94% and 18.39%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
